{"word":"G3891 - παρανομέω - paranoméō - par-an-om-eh'-o - Contrary to law","slug":"G3891","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρανομέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>paranoméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>par-an-om-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Contrary to law"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - paranomeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>par-an-om-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G3551\">G3551</a>; to <i>be opposed to law</i>, that is, to <i>transgress:</i> - contrary to law."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1772\">G1772</a>, <a href=\"#/G3544\">G3544</a>, <a href=\"#/G3545\">G3545</a>, <a href=\"#/G3547\">G3547</a>, <a href=\"#/G3548\">G3548</a>, <a href=\"#/G3549\">G3549</a>, <a href=\"#/G3550\">G3550</a>, <a href=\"#/G3551\">G3551</a>, <a href=\"#/G3892\">G3892</a>, <a href=\"#/G458\">G458</a>, <a href=\"#/G459\">G459</a>, <a href=\"#/G460\">G460</a>"}]}